Public universities, particularly the larger ones, are struggling under humongous debt. The reason universities are in this uncomfortable situation are well known.  Matters education have been dominating the headlines for all the wrong reasons lately – significant absenteeism after post-Covid-19 schools reopening, rampant pregnancies, inexplicable school fires, to cane or not to cane students, reports of mass failures in preparatory exams, etc. Not pretty at all.



